      "published": "31 Oct 2009, 15:00",
      "summary": "\"Teenage Dirtbag\" is a single by Wheatus, released in 2000. It was included on the soundtrack of the movie Loser. The single was massively successful in Australia, spending three weeks at #1 and becoming the second-highest selling single of the year. It also reached #2 in the United Kingdom and Germany. <a href=\"http://www.last.fm/music/Wheatus/_/Teenage+Dirtbag\">Read more on Last.fm</a>.",
